title: Team Sleep - The Complete Collection
description:
This is the complete discography of Team Sleep, who are back and finally recording their second album this fall. 

This torrent includes their self titled album from 2005, as well as several collections of demos that were leaked throughout the years from 2001-2007.

If you want to support the band you can purchase packages to be apart of the recording process in New York this October. 

Support the band, support the music. 

Rock on
